屌大家 永遠其他人d呀哥對細佬好好 反而自己果個呀哥就衰到仆街 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeffc420b87c54861c8da7fe21051f5e5a35f2d8","tid":27934,"uid":48358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T00:02:49.000Z","msg":"無呀哥 我就係呀哥"},{"pid":"070d5ec0360869e20a57eb7425dc22d22189cc05","tid":27934,"uid":3164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T00:06:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌我呀哥都會 仲會撩完鼻屎hi落我到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌我兩個呀哥都會 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  仲話乜撚嘢底褲超人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲會撩佢哋自己屎眼, 撩完俾我聞屎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84cfb4f55ade12154e5a870149524820fdae63e4","tid":27934,"uid":49414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T01:27:17.000Z","msg":"成日迫我幫佢打飛機,搞到我濕哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dd03dc030d2ab5d60a029db73acad515109351a","tid":27934,"uid":57695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T01:28:41.000Z","msg":"通常細佬企硬阿哥手軟"},{"pid":"e0fbfeec3a1256585128572c731973234b3c58f2","tid":27934,"uid":23972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T02:02:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就來三十歲都唔做野，要個做細佬既幫手養佢，做咩姐? 前世欠撚左佢咩？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我呀哥都就三十<br />\n又係唔做嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n痴撚線 我仲讀緊書冇收入嗰陣佢已經成日問我借錢<br />\n有乜理由咁大個人仲攤大手板問屋企人借錢<br />\n有時仲要偷錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n借到我家姐block埋佢電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔肯借畀佢佢就發癲  狂掉嘢<br />\n有一次佢冇啦啦鬧我  仲要郁手打我  老母已經係咁㩒住佢<br />\n最後仲要話我用佢啲錢去讀書  實情係我冇問過屋企攞錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但佢唔撚信  仲要用啲隔夜飯嚟掉我  再趕我出門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n從此以後都唔會再成日留係屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6afc49b786f942ce1c47689d1e3ff369c65344e","tid":27934,"uid":52816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T02:16:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fb06d1f2658d52a20014c07f50a1a8dc6377d63a","tid":27934,"uid":21064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T02:22:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇留言10樣有9樣都中哂 是咪好仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18b6c8ecbed900d6ab0477688f45c62ab3b48ba0","tid":27934,"uid":37003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T02:26:42.000Z","msg":"一齊食飯搭車永遠無散紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n還錢比人就問我借<br />\n但係未還過比我 一句呢啲無得計就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n永遠話要返工 屋企野全部唔做等人做<br />\n然後比人嘖到佢無聲出就發老脾<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a18975a87fc1c03cda6afc7bf315491abfe803e","tid":27934,"uid":30835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T02:37:36.000Z","msg":"23歲垃圾廢青<br />\n番過幾份工<br />\n份份都係番一兩個月就突發唔番<br />\n人工都唔番去攞，要人捉撚住佢嚟屌再陪佢去攞<br />\n現時日日係屋企打機，唔番工<br />\n又食煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n偷鳩我錢（自此所財物我都跟身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n又偷鳩屋企人錢<br />\n需要你嗰時就好聲好氣<br />\n唔需要你就屌你老母<br />\n點解呢啲人仲未撚死<br />\n老母仲成日好聲好氣咁同佢講野<br />\n佢又下下爆哂粗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"623398fdd03cb8e5422adfa62e531971bc15ead3","tid":27934,"uid":44301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T03:06:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>朝早鬧鐘永遠早過我15分鐘響，但過左九個字甚至一個鐘我出門口佢都係未起身。 屌你老母日日想瞓多陣都唔撚得，比第二個人既鬧鐘嘈醒真係好撚嬲，下世投胎寧做毒撚都唔撚想要呀哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"322b8dbb616e75d28a672551cd19a129ad2a89bc","tid":27934,"uid":44301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T03:07:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>朝早鬧鐘永遠早過我15分鐘響，但過左九個字甚至一個鐘我出門口佢都係未起身。 屌你老母日日想瞓多陣都唔撚得，比第二個人既鬧鐘嘈醒真係好撚嬲，下世投胎寧做毒撚都唔撚想要呀哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屋企3個家姐同房<br />\n佢地鬧鐘永遠早過我<br />\n但我從來唔會比佢地嘈鬧<br />\n利申：自己個鬧鐘都唔會聽到<br />\n訓緊教會自己過濾"},{"pid":"dd093f8404f636add6b324750b4d050a233ad372","tid":27934,"uid":59945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T03:16:33.000Z","msg":"喺屋企食煙，我訓緊教都照食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96a6a403c25fb21905a7ef692599cba0f670d001","tid":27934,"uid":3206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T03:21:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有情緒病架佢"},{"pid":"4575c7116cf092512d3e591aaaea015f61c8a725","tid":27934,"uid":37922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T03:27:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7d48cff17add032ea608b390dab1e25c9d7a8d28","tid":27934,"uid":35906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T03:45:14.000Z","msg":"搞到我菊花鬆鬆哋"},{"pid":"94efaee7fa8e450c710ee3dfc047f4ec429a2be1","tid":27934,"uid":38790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T05:52:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一家人食飯唔比我講野 一開口佢勁大聲就同我疊聲<br />\n細個出街自己搵唔到底褲發脾氣搵野掟我<br />\n叫我起身係用枕頭一力兜頭心口碎大石咁拍落黎 痛到喊仲屌我煩<br />\n我習慣沖涼聽歌 有次沖緊果陣佢拍門話要拎牙刷 我聽唔到 無幫佢拎 剩係答左佢好快出黎<br />\n佢拳打腳踢廁所門 打到爆缸 最後搵鎚係出門打爆個門鎖<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a4787e9a44078a24afff7f67b509d516a9942be","tid":27934,"uid":13361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T16:11:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>23歲垃圾廢青<br />\n番過幾份工<br />\n份份都係番一兩個月就突發唔番<br />\n人工都唔番去攞，要人捉撚住佢嚟屌再陪佢去攞<br />\n現時日日係屋企打機，唔番工<br />\n又食煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n偷鳩我錢（自此所財物我都跟身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n又偷鳩屋企人錢<br />\n需要你嗰時就好聲好氣<br />\n唔需要你就屌你老母<br />\n點解呢啲人仲未撚死<br />\n老母仲成日好聲好氣咁同佢講野<br />\n佢又下下爆哂粗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢樣正 需要你時細佬前細佬後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a32948fbab29d0052ac69c8d8e6af41e1e5fc586","tid":27934,"uid":14447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T16:43:36.000Z","msg":"真係好撚憎佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}